import React from "react";

const ArchiveIcon = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="43"
      height="43"
      viewBox="0 0 43 43"
    >
      <g id="Groupe_14" data-name="Groupe 14" transform="translate(-94 -176)">
        <rect
          id="Rectangle_12"
          data-name="Rectangle 12"
          width="43"
          height="43"
          transform="translate(94 176)"
          fill="rgba(255,255,255,0)"
        />
        <g
          id="Icon_feather-archive"
          data-name="Icon feather-archive"
          transform="translate(105.5 186.5)"
        >
          <path
            id="Tracé_15"
            data-name="Tracé 15"
            d="M18.378,12V22.023H4.5V12"
            transform="translate(-1.458 -3.645)"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#3d3939"
            strokeLinecap="round"
            strokeLinejoin="round"
            strokeWidth="1.2"
          />
          <path
            id="Tracé_16"
            data-name="Tracé 16"
            d="M1.5,4.5H18.461V8.355H1.5Z"
            transform="translate(0 0)"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#3d3939"
            strokeLinecap="round"
            strokeLinejoin="round"
            strokeWidth="1.2"
          />
          <path
            id="Tracé_17"
            data-name="Tracé 17"
            d="M15,18h3.084"
            transform="translate(-6.561 -6.561)"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#3d3939"
            strokeLinecap="round"
            strokeLinejoin="round"
            strokeWidth="1.2"
          />
        </g>
      </g>
    </svg>
  );
};

export default ArchiveIcon;
